        <div rend="slide">
          <head>A simple example (1)</head>
          <p><graphic url="../Graphics/Genetic/Ms629_p05-dtl-1.png" width="360px"/>. </p>
          <p>Editorial strategy may be simply to note that we have expanded the abbreviations:
              <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
